import { NavLink } from "react-router-dom";
import {
  Home,
  Receipt,
  BarChart3,
  Wallet,
  Bell,
  User,
  Settings,
  LogOut,
  Plus
} from "lucide-react";
import '../../styles/Sidebar.css';

const Sidebar = ({ activeTab, onTabChange, onLogout }) => {
  return (
    <aside className="sidebar">
      <button onClick={() => onTabChange("dashboard")}>
        Dashboard
      </button>

      <button onClick={() => onTabChange("expenses")}>
        Expenses
      </button>

      <button onClick={() => onTabChange("analytics")}>
        Reports
      </button>

      <button onClick={() => onTabChange("budgets")}>
        Budgets
      </button>

      <button onClick={() => onTabChange("profile")}>
        Profile
      </button>

      <button onClick={onLogout}>
        Logout
      </button>
    </aside>
  );
};
